          "text": "下书人当面。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下书人与爷叩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下书人，你叫什么名字？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我叫大胆黄文。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你的胆有多大？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有巴斗大。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周仓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "剖腹看者！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀爷呀，我的胆没那么大，有荠莱仔那么大。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何能大能小？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀，能强能弱我的爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "收！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周仓收刀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可有书信？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "书信呈上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是鲁大夫请某过江赴会。俺这里修书不及，原书发回。回去奏明你家爷，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "出去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄文",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日吓破黄文胆，再也不做下书人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好怕，好怕。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄文下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掩门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掩门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖大开门〗。四龙套自两边分下，关羽转小座。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父王，那书信上写的什么言语，说与臣儿知道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿听者。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（石榴花） 上写着，两朝相隔汉阳江。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "安排什么来？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（斗鹌鹁） 安排下，打凤的牢笼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "古来筵无好筵，会无好会，还是不去的是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，周仓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他那里兵多将广。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他那里人强马壮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大江遥远，恐难接应。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还是先下手为强。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关平，明日驾定小舟，江口伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周仓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明日随某赴会者。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（尾声） 虽不比，临潼会上秦穆公，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
        }
      ],
